The paper proposes a vision-based solution for indoor localization of autonomous driving in parking lots, which involves computer vision, robotics, artificial intelligence, machine learning, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
